A security guard has been killed in a cash-in-transit heist on the N2 near Empangeni on Monday .It is reported that the incident took place around 08:20am when four suspects stopped security guards demanding money.Colonel Thembeka Mbhele said four men shot the security and took money which is believed to be 20 thousand.He added: suspects fled with grey Hyundai I35 and no arrest has been made .A case of armed robbery has been open at Empangeni police station as police.TNA Reporter 